        <h1>User Manual</h1>
        <p>Welcome to LINGO VIBE!!!<br>
          Welcome to the Voice AI Translator! This application translates spoken Tamil into English text and reads it out loud. It is designed to be user-friendly and efficient, leveraging speech recognition, translation, and text-to-speech technologies.
           <br>
           
           
           </p>
