          <div class="de1">
            <h2>Trouble Shoot Requirements</h2>
            <p> 
              <ol>
                <li><b>No Text in Textbox:</b> Ensure your microphone is working and the browser has permission to use it. Speak clearly and loudly.</li>
                <li><b>Internet connection.</b></li>
                <li><b>Python 3.x installed on your machine</b></li>
                <li><b>Required Python libraries:</b> Flask, translate, gtts, SpeechRecognition, pyaudio</li>
                
              </ol>
              
            </p>
